comments.author: Reincarnated.1754
comments.body:
If you are using MS Edge web browser, you have to force new cashed tiles.

Go settings.
Click: “Choose what to clear” under: clear browsing data.
Select: cashed data and files.
Then press: Clear.

When done refresh you web page.

I had this problem the last time we had new tiles.
